    <title>Refugees contributor: Giacomo Zandonini</title>
    <description>Giacomo Zandonini is an Italian freelance journalist. He has contributed to La Repubblica, International, Left, Vanity Fair, Women Under Siege, Radio Vaticana and other newspapers. He deals with migration, human trafficking, politics and society in the Sahel. In 2016 he worked for the documentary Wallah – Je Te Jure, produced by IOM Niger, for Ai Weiwei Film Studio and Open Society Foundations.
</description>
